weight: 400;\"> 1.5 n\u0103m (Ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc kho\u1ea3ng 2,5 n\u0103m)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p trung c\u1ea5p: 1.5 <\/span><b>&#8211; <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 n\u0103m.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>4. L\u00ea\u0323 phi\u0301<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1: mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n: Ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc <\/span><b>2.500.000\u0111<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\/1 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1;<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0C\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c: <\/span><b>1.200.000\u0111<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\/1 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>5. H\u00f4\u0300 s\u01a1<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Phi\u1ebfu \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi (theo m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4);<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT;<\/span><\/li>\